639
00:40:02,149 --> 00:40:05,584
By any chance, did you pay money to get such textbook arguments...

640
00:40:05,680 --> 00:40:07,710
such as the importance of self-realization...

641
00:40:08,050 --> 00:40:09,605
and community services?

642
00:40:14,060 --> 00:40:16,312
Why don't you be honest and think about it?

643
00:40:16,359 --> 00:40:18,824
Let's say there's a job that doesn't pay you a single penny...

644
00:40:18,930 --> 00:40:21,495
but that's self-fulfilling and helps with community services.

645
00:40:22,100 --> 00:40:23,181
Would you...

646
00:40:24,800 --> 00:40:25,880
actually...

647
00:40:27,570 --> 00:40:28,650
choose that job?

648
00:40:31,940 --> 00:40:34,549
This is why money should be our standard when choosing a job.

649
00:40:34,550 --> 00:40:37,849
My name is Yoon Seung Woo, and that is the end...

650
00:40:37,850 --> 00:40:39,162
of Wildflower Class' final statement.

