678
00:42:20,790 --> 00:42:22,506
That's the reason for this result.

679
00:42:25,090 --> 00:42:27,857
I'm going to make an official complaint.

680
00:42:28,790 --> 00:42:31,992
Ask yourself what exactly the complaint is about.

681
00:42:32,830 --> 00:42:34,719
Make sure it's not something you'll embarrass yourself with.

682
00:42:40,710 --> 00:42:42,790
