755
00:47:15,109 --> 00:47:17,009
I heard Lee Chae Min talking about it.

756
00:47:17,010 --> 00:47:18,678
We have four more intramural contests,

757
00:47:18,679 --> 00:47:20,498
but I never thought holding them could cause trouble.

758
00:47:20,580 --> 00:47:22,618
Are you saying the parents of Ivy Class...

