800
00:49:16,330 --> 00:49:18,389
(The related judge will receive disciplinary action,)

801
00:49:20,300 --> 00:49:22,188
(and the final winning team will change to Ivy Class.)

802
00:49:22,669 --> 00:49:23,679
Darn it.

803
00:49:26,139 --> 00:49:27,998
Don't get worked up.

804
00:49:28,280 --> 00:49:32,157
You have to take revenge rationally. You know that.

805
00:49:34,250 --> 00:49:36,038
This is the evidence we need.

806
00:49:36,689 --> 00:49:39,114
Bok Su, follow the plan.

807
00:49:44,530 --> 00:49:45,898
Darn.

808
00:49:45,899 --> 00:49:49,029
Are you kidding me? We beat Ivy Class good yesterday.

809
00:49:49,030 --> 00:49:52,070
We did, and they probably didn't like that.

810
00:49:52,240 --> 00:49:55,239
I overheard something yesterday,

811
00:49:55,439 --> 00:49:57,708
and apparently the kids from Ivy Class gave the school money.

812
00:49:57,709 --> 00:49:58,791
They bribed?

813
00:50:00,609 --> 00:50:01,608
What?

814
00:50:01,609 --> 00:50:03,579
You startled me. When did you get here?

815
00:50:03,580 --> 00:50:04,590
Is this the truth?

816
00:50:05,219 --> 00:50:06,718
All intramural contests...

817
00:50:06,719 --> 00:50:09,275
are held for Ivy Class and their student records.

818
00:50:10,590 --> 00:50:12,004
I never paid.

819
00:50:12,419 --> 00:50:14,339
Not you, but your mom probably did.

820
00:50:18,230 --> 00:50:21,361
Here. Eat this and calm down.

821
00:50:21,500 --> 00:50:22,883
Don't ruin your own name.

822
00:50:25,939 --> 00:50:27,758
Did you say I made an error when evaluating the debate?

823
00:50:28,010 --> 00:50:30,739
I did it precisely and fairly.

824
00:50:30,740 --> 00:50:32,009
How can the school...

825
00:50:32,010 --> 00:50:34,479
strip away the rights of a teacher?

826
00:50:34,480 --> 00:50:37,408
Exactly. You shouldn't have evaluated them...

827
00:50:37,409 --> 00:50:39,579
according to your own criteria.

828
00:50:39,580 --> 00:50:42,580
Don't you know you shouldn't have marked them that way?

829
00:50:43,719 --> 00:50:45,609
Do you really not get it?

830
00:50:47,590 --> 00:50:48,741
I'll make...

831
00:50:49,389 --> 00:50:51,259
an official complaint to the chairman.

832
00:50:51,260 --> 00:50:54,499
You have so much energy even at your age.

833
00:50:54,500 --> 00:50:57,025
You should quit this job and go into farming.

834
00:50:57,199 --> 00:51:00,769
You can do something more productive with that energy.

835
00:51:00,770 --> 00:51:02,325
This place will run well...

836
00:51:03,240 --> 00:51:04,280
even without you.

837
00:51:21,230 --> 00:51:23,653
Bok Su, Mr. Park is in trouble.

838
00:51:23,859 --> 00:51:26,182
He went to argue with Se Ho.

839
00:51:31,939 --> 00:51:33,888
I'll talk to the chairman.

840
00:51:36,109 --> 00:51:37,251
No, Ms. Son.

841
00:51:37,369 --> 00:51:38,722
I'll take care of this.

842
00:51:39,939 --> 00:51:41,424
It's about my students.

843
00:51:42,050 --> 00:51:44,504
Wildflower Class is my class.

844
00:51:46,080 --> 00:51:48,289
Rather than the judge,

845
00:51:48,290 --> 00:51:50,440
I should make an official complaint as the homeroom teacher.

846
00:52:11,580 --> 00:52:14,610
Right. Speak calmly.

847
00:52:14,750 --> 00:52:17,810
Be logical and consistent. Don't get worked up.

848
00:52:18,320 --> 00:52:19,693
You can do it, Soo Jeong.

849
00:52:27,459 --> 00:52:28,903
Hey, you crazy jerk.

850
00:52:31,959 --> 00:52:34,221
Are you done? Do you want some tea?

851
00:52:40,199 --> 00:52:41,209
Mr. Chairman.

852
00:52:42,209 --> 00:52:45,008
Please change this nonsensical decision.

853
00:52:45,209 --> 00:52:47,976
You know Wildflower Class won fair and square.

854
00:52:49,449 --> 00:52:52,176
The result being changed by one person's judging criteria,

855
00:52:52,449 --> 00:52:53,948
is that fair and square?

856
00:52:53,949 --> 00:52:55,031
Then,

857
00:52:55,149 --> 00:52:57,019
changing the result...

858
00:52:57,020 --> 00:53:00,050
to let the pre-arranged winner win, is that fair and square?

859
00:53:00,459 --> 00:53:02,529
You're making a risky comment without any proof.

860
00:53:02,530 --> 00:53:04,075
You know it's true.

861
00:53:04,429 --> 00:53:06,458
Is teaching an unfair defeat to the kids...

862
00:53:06,459 --> 00:53:07,913
your philosophy?

863
00:53:08,770 --> 00:53:11,366
You said you'd correct Seolsong.

864
00:53:11,570 --> 00:53:13,185
You asked me to watch.

865
00:53:14,369 --> 00:53:17,299
From now on, I'm going to correct...

866
00:53:17,669 --> 00:53:19,326
all the wrong things that have settled in Seolsong High School.

867
00:53:23,780 --> 00:53:24,930
Soo Jeong. You are...

868
00:53:25,780 --> 00:53:27,900
in no position to stand up straight.

869
00:53:29,320 --> 00:53:30,430
What about Kim Myung Ho?

870
00:53:30,719 --> 00:53:32,275
What will you do about that?

871
00:53:37,490 --> 00:53:39,176
Fine. What about you?

872
00:53:39,859 --> 00:53:41,749
Is your conscience clear?

873
00:53:42,070 --> 00:53:43,545
Where did all that money go?

874
00:53:43,669 --> 00:53:44,938
It went to you or your mother.

875
00:53:44,939 --> 00:53:45,979
That's right.

876
00:53:46,669 --> 00:53:48,457
So we're accomplices.

877
00:53:49,139 --> 00:53:51,503
You can't hate me like this when we're in this together.

878
00:53:52,240 --> 00:53:53,693
Don't touch my kids.

879
00:53:54,949 --> 00:53:57,648
That's right. Because of that petty money,

880
00:53:57,649 --> 00:54:00,019
I sold my conscience, so I can't hold my head up high.

881
00:54:00,020 --> 00:54:01,293
But if you do anything to the kids,

882
00:54:03,050 --> 00:54:04,635
that'll be the end for both of us.

883
00:54:05,560 --> 00:54:07,035
I won't go down alone.

884
00:54:12,159 --> 00:54:13,342
I mean...

885
00:54:14,699 --> 00:54:15,829
"Leave the kids alone."

886
00:54:15,830 --> 00:54:17,749
"Leave Bok Su alone." Then...

887
00:54:19,939 --> 00:54:21,051
what should I do?

888
00:54:22,969 --> 00:54:24,051
I...

889
00:54:25,340 --> 00:54:27,127
I made a mistake,

890
00:54:27,310 --> 00:54:28,795
so I deserve this.

891
00:54:29,810 --> 00:54:31,537
But the kids didn't do anything wrong.

892
00:54:31,719 --> 00:54:33,466
Bok Su also didn't do anything wrong.

893
00:54:34,550 --> 00:54:36,812
And you know that, you crazy jerk.

894
00:54:42,929 --> 00:54:46,293
You should know that the more you act like this...

895
00:54:48,530 --> 00:54:49,611
the more I want to get rid of Bok Su.

896
00:54:52,469 --> 00:54:54,116
Try it, you crazy jerk.

897
00:54:54,909 --> 00:54:57,263
I'll show you who's crazier.

898
00:55:06,919 --> 00:55:09,919
(Counseling Room)

899
00:55:28,909 --> 00:55:30,859
Why are you still here?

900
00:55:33,609 --> 00:55:35,629
Mr. Park told me.

901
00:55:38,820 --> 00:55:39,890
Are you okay?

902
00:55:49,030 --> 00:55:50,403
Bok Su.

903
00:55:51,760 --> 00:55:54,223
You look so good in uniform.

904
00:55:57,730 --> 00:55:58,750
I...

905
00:56:00,399 --> 00:56:02,732
really want to help you graduate.

906
00:56:12,149 --> 00:56:13,291
Don't worry.

907
00:56:15,050 --> 00:56:17,170
I'll get the diploma myself.

908
00:56:17,649 --> 00:56:20,347
I want you...

909
00:56:20,659 --> 00:56:21,801
to give me the diploma, okay?

910
00:56:27,699 --> 00:56:29,143
What am I going to do?

911
00:56:30,730 --> 00:56:33,598
I want to stand up to Se Ho.

912
00:56:34,669 --> 00:56:38,548
But because of my mistake, I can't even fight him.

913
00:56:42,480 --> 00:56:44,601
I really regret what I did in the past.

914
00:57:46,010 --> 00:57:47,293
(Counseling Room)

915
00:58:23,810 --> 00:58:28,799
(My Strange Hero)

916
00:58:42,800 --> 00:58:44,938
It's not a school. It's a corporation.

917
00:58:44,939 --> 00:58:46,269
Is this all true?

918
00:58:46,270 --> 00:58:48,509
Mr. Park sent an anonymous letter to the Education Office?

919
00:58:48,510 --> 00:58:50,908
Stop tarnishing my school and leave!

920
00:58:50,909 --> 00:58:52,408
It's my school now.

921
00:58:52,409 --> 00:58:54,378
If you want to kick me out, wait. Or take it away from me.

922
00:58:54,379 --> 00:58:56,509
I'm a teacher. What should I do?

923
00:58:56,510 --> 00:58:57,549
Don't worry.

924
00:58:57,550 --> 00:58:58,718
I'll take care of it. Trust me.

925
00:58:58,719 --> 00:58:59,749
Call the School Violence Prevention Committee.

926
00:58:59,750 --> 00:59:01,349
Transfer him to another school.

927
00:59:01,350 --> 00:59:03,049
- If you do this suddenly... - It was refused.

928
00:59:03,050 --> 00:59:05,989
My good intentions were refused. So I'll have to force them.

929
00:59:05,990 --> 00:59:07,319
Umbrella. Don't you have an umbrella?

930
00:59:07,320 --> 00:59:08,559
Are you crazy? We're in school.

931
00:59:08,560 --> 00:59:09,989
- You're in school uniform. - Uniform isn't a problem.

932
00:59:09,990 --> 00:59:12,329
Are you sure you won't let her get hurt?

933
00:59:12,330 --> 00:59:14,029
I'll never let her be alone.

934
00:59:14,030 --> 00:59:16,099
I want to be a teacher like you.

935
00:59:16,100 --> 00:59:18,099
Mr. Park did it, didn't he?

936
00:59:18,100 --> 00:59:19,339
I'm the evidence of...

937
00:59:19,340 --> 00:59:20,839
your failure as a teacher.

938
00:59:20,840 --> 00:59:23,667
As the board chairman, I'll fire Mr. Park.

